<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 255); text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-shadow: none; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(192, 80, 77); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“万城初晓一幕白</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 255); text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-shadow: none; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(192, 80, 77); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">千山云雀皆可爱”</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 80, 77); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">跟随我院辅导员</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 255); text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-shadow: none; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(192, 80, 77); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">一起来运动吧</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240417/1713367057014028074.png" title="1713367057014028074.png" alt="image.png" width="430" height="234" style="width: 430px; height: 234px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">每人手持一根锣锤，需蒙眼去敲锣，然后接力给下一个人，这一根锣锤仿佛是辅导员之间友谊的桥梁。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240417/1713367076546017603.png" title="1713367076546017603.png" alt="image.png" width="389" height="248" style="width: 389px; height: 248px;"/></p>